2015-08-04  Mark Schilfgaarde  <ms4@phpdl1.ph.kcl.ac.uk>

	* Bug fix: prior versions calculated the envelope shape of deep local orbitals from the spin-1 potential
          This results in some inconsistencies.  It now uses a spin-averaged potential.  See new check fp/test/test.fp fept
          The old behavior can be mimicked by adding 40 to HAM_AUTOBAS_PFLOAT.
	
